	measure 'NLVH Actual TKKD' = ```
			
			VAR _shops =
			    VALUES('DIM_Danh mục_Phòng ban'[Cửa hàng])
			RETURN
			CALCULATE(
			    AVERAGE('adhoc_tkkd'[% Thực đạt TKKD]),
			    TREATAS(_shops, 'adhoc_tkkd'[Cửa hàng])
			)
			
			```
		lineageTag: 1734514b-a82a-4fdd-a5a6-8d8c8ad93240

